## Relay-D4 TokenBudget Enforcement
**Status:** implemented
**Module:** `crates/auto-forge/src/relay/budget.rs`
**Tags:** stack:backend
**Depends on:** Runtime-G2

```rust
pub struct TokenBudget {
    pub limit: u64,
    pub warning_at: u64,
    pub strategy: BudgetStrategy,
}

pub enum BudgetStrategy {
    HardStop,
    EscalateModel,
    SummarizeContext,
    SkipOptional,
}

pub struct BudgetTracker {
    pub run_budget: TokenBudget,
    pub step_budgets: HashMap<String, TokenBudget>,
    pub cumulative: u64,
    pub per_step: HashMap<String, u64>,
}

impl BudgetTracker {
    /// Record token usage from an API response.
    pub fn record(&mut self, step: &str, input: u64, output: u64);

    /// Check if current spend triggers any budget action.
    pub fn check(&self, step: &str) -> BudgetAction;

    /// Estimate "parallel cost" for analytics.
    pub fn estimate_parallel_cost(&self, num_agents: u32, avg_context: u64) -> u64;
}

pub enum BudgetAction {
    None,
    Warning { remaining: u64 },
    Compress,
    HardStop,
}
```

| Field | Type | Description |
|---|---|---|
| `limit` | `u64` | Hard token limit |
| `warning_at` | `u64` | Percentage (0-1) of limit where warning fires |
| `strategy` | `BudgetStrategy` | Action when limit reached |
| `cumulative` | `u64` | Total tokens this run |
| `per_step` | `HashMap` | Tokens per profession/step |

